* {{ill|lt=Jowa (Japan)|Q1075605|WD=Q1075605|lt=Jowa|1=Jōwa (Heian period)}} On April 17, 13 years ({{ill|lt=846|Q30454|WD=Q30454|1=846}}), he was entrusted to the Meishin as a junior fifth rank, lower rank, and eighth rank.
